{"tid":1485992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵車長罷工，不合作運動係咪可以轉玩法？","createTime":"2019-08-18T17:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T23:59:52.000Z","uid":173106,"like":165,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab94794b8fbdfa9364f644cd613f56ca1cfc51e","tid":1485992,"uid":173106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:37:56.000Z","msg":"聽日港鐵車長罷工係因為港鐵冇回應到佢地聯署嘅訴求，包括譴責警方喺地鐵入面妄顧安全而作出嘅驅散行為<br />\n<br />\n咁如果聽日真係出現塞鐵，希望大家可以俾返個焦點喺港鐵車長罷工嘅原因到，而唔係因為示威者嘅不合作運動而搞到塞鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔塞車門，大家可以做啲咩呢？<br />\n香港人好團結架嘛<br />\n大家咪齊齊去地鐵站聲援吓，舉吓牌支持車長罷工囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人等車返工又有人去聲援<br />\n咁咪好多人喺地鐵站入面囉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁太多人都辦法架喇，咪順便做吓文宣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔搞串人哋個party之餘，又可以達到效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試一試，如果唔得咪還原基本步囉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">第一次開post麻煩屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"aadae0f4577b4d818b7b0b24efc116ca1d85aea1","tid":1485992,"uid":173106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:38:23.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"c1a0c4bb01a5c2a067187f23376bd81889268f24","tid":1485992,"uid":173106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:38:33.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"62eb3ec4ea9375f0c334fa0ba6e476b4bb1900dc","tid":1485992,"uid":51041,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"824 和你塞"},{"pid":"3ca193e7b4bc7df08e0bb522a246751f894a3774","tid":1485992,"uid":173106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8a71f0c9b16519ccce8fc8f2ba4fe8445f13c27b","tid":1485992,"uid":173106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:38:57.000Z","msg":"3"