uote":{"pid":"6ab94794b8fbdfa9364f644cd613f56ca1cfc51e","tid":1485992,"uid":173106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:37:56.000Z","msg":"聽日港鐵車長罷工係因為港鐵冇回應到佢地聯署嘅訴求，包括譴責警方喺地鐵入面妄顧安全而作出嘅驅散行為<br />\n<br />\n咁如果聽日真係出現塞鐵，希望大家可以俾返個焦點喺港鐵車長罷工嘅原因到，而唔係因為示威者嘅不合作運動而搞到塞鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔塞車門，大家可以做啲咩呢？<br />\n香港人好團結架嘛<br />\n大家咪齊齊去地鐵站聲援吓，舉吓牌支持車長罷工囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人等車返工又有人去聲援<br />\n咁咪好多人喺地鐵站入面囉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁太多人都辦法架喇，咪順便做吓文宣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔搞串人哋個party之餘，又可以達到效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試一試，如果唔得咪還原基本步囉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">第一次開post麻煩屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:27:58.000Z","msg":"總之唔好搶人風頭啦"},{"pid":"7b859790c7d375e97be381c4d487272bf86ed290","tid":1485992,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9b3c70113e81d67cc882f8cfd24fb818c1bdaaa","tid":1485992,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:54:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得目前唔好將車長拖落反送中運動入面, 佢地聽日罷工係為左切身利益去做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:29:41.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"afaf32514d0d9d1a4ae622e317d95a5349a5db9c","tid":1485992,"uid":192455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:30:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f11c43287182c347452298d6fc80c016a6a7bca9","tid":1485992,"uid":67756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:30:57.000Z","msg":"焦點比返車長好啲"},{"pid":"b7f14ad681696cf09461ef8b62402681d15d5e52","tid":1485992,"uid":60451,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T18:31:57.000Z","msg":"主場係車長 唔洗搞咁多嘢<br />\n如果想助攻緊係主動接受記者訪問"},{"pid":"89289115fc9c094c11a437f6018c53669167172e","tid":14859